9AOT_define Situation :: ‹τ ⇒ φ› (‹Situation'(_')›)
10  situations: ‹Situation(x) ≡⇩d⇩f A!x & ∀F (x[F] → Propositional([F]))›
11
12AOT_theorem "T-sit": ‹TruthValue(x) → Situation(x)›
13proof(rule "→I")
14  AOT_assume ‹TruthValue(x)›
15  AOT_hence ‹∃p TruthValueOf(x,p)›
16    using "T-value"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
17  then AOT_obtain p where ‹TruthValueOf(x,p)› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
18  AOT_hence θ: ‹A!x & ∀F (x[F] ≡ ∃q((q ≡ p) & F = [λy q]))›
19    using "tv-p"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
20  AOT_show ‹Situation(x)›
21  proof(rule situations[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"]; safe intro!: "&I" GEN "→I" θ[THEN "&E"(1)])
22    fix F
23    AOT_assume ‹x[F]›
24    AOT_hence ‹∃q((q ≡ p) & F = [λy q])›
25      using θ[THEN "&E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=F], THEN "≡E"(1)] by argo
26    then AOT_obtain q where ‹(q ≡ p) & F = [λy q]› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
27    AOT_hence ‹∃p F = [λy p]› using "&E"(2) "∃I"(2) by metis
28    AOT_thus ‹Propositional([F])›
29      by (metis "≡⇩d⇩fI" "prop-prop1")
30  qed
31qed

33AOT_theorem "possit-sit:1": ‹Situation(x) ≡ □Situation(x)›
34proof(rule "≡I"; rule "→I")
35  AOT_assume ‹Situation(x)›
36  AOT_hence 0: ‹A!x & ∀F (x[F] → Propositional([F]))›
37    using situations[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
38  AOT_have 1: ‹□(A!x & ∀F (x[F] → Propositional([F])))›
39  proof(rule "KBasic:3"[THEN "≡E"(2)]; rule "&I")
40    AOT_show ‹□A!x› using 0[THEN "&E"(1)] by (metis "oa-facts:2"[THEN "→E"])
41  next
42    AOT_have ‹∀F (x[F] → Propositional([F])) → □∀F (x[F] → Propositional([F]))›
43      by (AOT_subst ‹Propositional([F])› ‹∃p (F = [λy p])› for: F :: ‹<κ>›)
44         (auto simp: "prop-prop1" "≡Df" "enc-prop-nec:2")
45    AOT_thus ‹□∀F (x[F] → Propositional([F]))›
46      using 0[THEN "&E"(2)] "→E" by blast
47  qed
48  AOT_show ‹□Situation(x)›
49    by (AOT_subst ‹Situation(x)› ‹A!x & ∀F (x[F] → Propositional([F]))›)
50       (auto simp: 1 "≡Df" situations)
51next
52  AOT_show ‹Situation(x)› if ‹□Situation(x)›
53    using "qml:2"[axiom_inst, THEN "→E", OF that].
54qed

58  by (metis "RE◇" "S5Basic:2" "≡E"(1) "≡E"(5) "Commutativity of ≡")

61  using "possit-sit:1" "possit-sit:2" by (meson "≡E"(5))

64  by (meson "Act-Basic:5" "Act-Sub:2" "RA[2]" "≡E"(1) "≡E"(6) "possit-sit:2")

66AOT_theorem "possit-sit:5": ‹Situation(∘p)›
67proof (safe intro!: situations[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" GEN "→I" "prop-prop1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"])
68  AOT_have ‹∃F ∘p[F]›
69    using "tv-id:2"[THEN "prop-enc"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"], THEN "&E"(2)]
70          "existential:1" "prop-prop2:2" by blast
71  AOT_thus ‹A!∘p›
72    by (safe intro!: "encoders-are-abstract"[unvarify x, THEN "→E"]
73                     "t=t-proper:2"[THEN "→E", OF "ext-p-tv:3"])
74next
75  fix F
76  AOT_assume ‹∘p[F]›
77  AOT_hence ‹❙ιx(A!x & ∀F (x[F] ≡ ∃q ((q ≡ p) & F = [λy q])))[F]›
78    using "tv-id:1" "rule=E" by fast
79  AOT_hence ‹❙𝒜∃q ((q ≡ p) & F = [λy q])›
80    using "≡E"(1) "desc-nec-encode:1" by fast
81  AOT_hence ‹∃q ❙𝒜((q ≡ p) & F = [λy q])›
82    by (metis "Act-Basic:10" "≡E"(1))
83  then AOT_obtain q where ‹❙𝒜((q ≡ p) & F = [λy q])› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
84  AOT_hence ‹❙𝒜F = [λy q]› by (metis "Act-Basic:2" "con-dis-i-e:2:b" "intro-elim:3:a")
85  AOT_hence ‹F = [λy q]›
86    using "id-act:1"[unvarify β, THEN "≡E"(2)] by (metis "prop-prop2:2")
87  AOT_thus ‹∃p F = [λy p]›
88    using "∃I" by fast
89qed

91AOT_theorem "possit-sit:6": ‹Situation(⊤)›
92proof -
93  AOT_have true_def: ‹❙⊢⇩□ ⊤ = ❙ιx (A!x & ∀F (x[F] ≡ ∃p(p & F = [λy p])))›
94    by (simp add: "A-descriptions" "rule-id-df:1[zero]" "the-true:1")
95  AOT_hence true_den: ‹❙⊢⇩□ ⊤↓›
96    using "t=t-proper:1" "vdash-properties:6" by blast
97  AOT_have ‹❙𝒜TruthValue(⊤)›
98    using "actual-desc:2"[unvarify x, OF true_den, THEN "→E", OF true_def]
99    using "TV-lem2:1"[unvarify x, OF true_den, THEN "RA[2]",
100                      THEN "act-cond"[THEN "→E"], THEN "→E"]
101    by blast
102  AOT_hence ‹❙𝒜Situation(⊤)›
103    using "T-sit"[unvarify x, OF true_den, THEN "RA[2]",
104                  THEN "act-cond"[THEN "→E"], THEN "→E"] by blast
105  AOT_thus ‹Situation(⊤)›
106    using "possit-sit:4"[unvarify x, OF true_den, THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
107qed

127AOT_register_rigid_restricted_type
128  Situation: ‹Situation(κ)›
129proof
130  AOT_modally_strict {
131    fix p
132    AOT_obtain x where ‹TruthValueOf(x,p)›
133      by (metis "instantiation" "p-has-!tv:1")
134    AOT_hence ‹∃p TruthValueOf(x,p)› by (rule "∃I")
135    AOT_hence ‹TruthValue(x)› by (metis "≡⇩d⇩fI" "T-value")
136    AOT_hence ‹Situation(x)› using "T-sit"[THEN "→E"] by blast
137    AOT_thus ‹∃x Situation(x)› by (rule "∃I")
138  }
139next
140  AOT_modally_strict {
141    AOT_show ‹Situation(κ) → κ↓› for κ
142    proof (rule "→I")
143      AOT_assume ‹Situation(κ)›
144      AOT_hence ‹A!κ› by (metis "≡⇩d⇩fE" "&E"(1) situations)
145      AOT_thus ‹κ↓› by (metis "russell-axiom[exe,1].ψ_denotes_asm")
146    qed
147  }
148next
149  AOT_modally_strict {
150    fix α
151    AOT_show ‹□(Situation(α) → □Situation(α))›
152      using "possit-sit:1"[THEN "conventions:3"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"],
153                           THEN "&E"(1), THEN RN] by blast
154  }
155qed

160AOT_define TruthInSituation :: ‹τ ⇒ φ ⇒ φ› ("(_ ⊨/ _)" [100, 40] 100)
161  "true-in-s": ‹s ⊨ p ≡⇩d⇩f s❙Σp›
162
163notepad
164begin
165  (* Verify precedence. *)
166  fix x p q
167  have ‹«x ⊨ p → q» = «(x ⊨ p) → q»›
168    by simp
169  have ‹«x ⊨ p & q» = «(x ⊨ p) & q»›
170    by simp
171  have ‹«x ⊨ ¬p» = «x ⊨ (¬p)»›
172    by simp
173  have ‹«x ⊨ □p» = «x ⊨ (□p)»›
174    by simp
175  have ‹«x ⊨ ❙𝒜p» = «x ⊨ (❙𝒜p)»›
176    by simp
177  have ‹«□x ⊨ p» = «□(x ⊨ p)»›
178    by simp
179  have ‹«¬x ⊨ p» = «¬(x ⊨ p)»›
180    by simp
181end

184AOT_theorem lem1: ‹Situation(x) → (x ⊨ p ≡ x[λy p])›
185proof (rule "→I"; rule "≡I"; rule "→I")
186  AOT_assume ‹Situation(x)›
187  AOT_assume ‹x ⊨ p›
188  AOT_hence ‹x❙Σp›
189    using "true-in-s"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast
190  AOT_thus ‹x[λy p]› using "prop-enc"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast
191next
192  AOT_assume 1: ‹Situation(x)›
193  AOT_assume ‹x[λy p]›
194  AOT_hence ‹x❙Σp›
195    using "prop-enc"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI", OF "&I", OF "cqt:2"(1)] by blast
196  AOT_thus ‹x ⊨ p›
197    using "true-in-s"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] 1 "&I" by blast
198qed

200AOT_theorem "lem2:1": ‹s ⊨ p ≡ □s ⊨ p›
201proof -
202  AOT_have sit: ‹Situation(s)›
203    by (simp add: Situation.ψ)
204  AOT_have ‹s ⊨ p ≡ s[λy p]›
205    using lem1[THEN "→E", OF sit] by blast
206  also AOT_have ‹… ≡ □s[λy p]›
207    by (rule "en-eq:2[1]"[unvarify F]) "cqt:2[lambda]"
208  also AOT_have ‹… ≡ □s ⊨ p›
209    using lem1[THEN RM, THEN "→E", OF "possit-sit:1"[THEN "≡E"(1), OF sit]]
210    by (metis "KBasic:6" "≡E"(2) "Commutativity of ≡" "→E")
211  finally show ?thesis.
212qed
213
214AOT_theorem "lem2:2": ‹◇s ⊨ p ≡ s ⊨ p›
215proof -
216  AOT_have ‹□(s ⊨ p → □s ⊨ p)›
217    using "possit-sit:1"[THEN "≡E"(1), OF Situation.ψ]
218          "lem2:1"[THEN "conventions:3"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", THEN "&E"(1)]]
219          RM[OF "→I", THEN "→E"] by blast
220  thus ?thesis by (metis "B◇" "S5Basic:13" "T◇" "≡I" "≡E"(1) "→E")
221qed

223AOT_theorem "lem2:3": ‹◇s ⊨ p ≡ □s ⊨ p›
224  using "lem2:1" "lem2:2" by (metis "≡E"(5))

226AOT_theorem "lem2:4": ‹❙𝒜(s ⊨ p) ≡ s ⊨ p›
227proof -
228  AOT_have ‹□(s ⊨ p → □s ⊨ p)›
229    using "possit-sit:1"[THEN "≡E"(1), OF Situation.ψ]
230      "lem2:1"[THEN "conventions:3"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", THEN "&E"(1)]]
231      RM[OF "→I", THEN "→E"] by blast
232  thus ?thesis
233    using "sc-eq-fur:2"[THEN "→E"] by blast
234qed

236AOT_theorem "lem2:5": ‹¬s ⊨ p ≡ □¬s ⊨ p›
237  by (metis "KBasic2:1" "contraposition:1[2]" "→I" "≡I" "≡E"(3) "≡E"(4) "lem2:2")

239AOT_theorem "sit-identity": ‹s = s' ≡ ∀p(s ⊨ p ≡ s' ⊨ p)›
240proof(rule "≡I"; rule "→I")
241  AOT_assume ‹s = s'›
242  moreover AOT_have ‹∀p(s ⊨ p ≡ s ⊨ p)›
243    by (simp add: "oth-class-taut:3:a" "universal-cor")
244  ultimately AOT_show ‹∀p(s ⊨ p ≡ s' ⊨ p)›
245    using "rule=E" by fast
246next
247  AOT_assume a: ‹∀p (s ⊨ p ≡ s' ⊨ p)›
248  AOT_show ‹s = s'›
249  proof(safe intro!: "ab-obey:1"[THEN "→E", THEN "→E"] "&I" GEN "≡I" "→I")
250    AOT_show ‹A!s› using Situation.ψ "≡⇩d⇩fE" "&E"(1) situations by blast
251  next
252    AOT_show ‹A!s'› using Situation.ψ "≡⇩d⇩fE" "&E"(1) situations by blast
253  next
254    fix F
255    AOT_assume 0: ‹s[F]›
256    AOT_hence ‹∃p (F = [λy p])›
257      using Situation.ψ[THEN situations[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"], THEN "&E"(2),
258                        THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=F], THEN "→E"]
259            "prop-prop1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
260    then AOT_obtain p where F_def: ‹F = [λy p]›
261      using "∃E" by metis
262    AOT_hence ‹s[λy p]›
263      using 0 "rule=E" by blast
264    AOT_hence ‹s ⊨ p›
265      using lem1[THEN "→E", OF Situation.ψ, THEN "≡E"(2)] by blast
266    AOT_hence ‹s' ⊨ p›
267      using a[THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=p], THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
268    AOT_hence ‹s'[λy p]›
269      using lem1[THEN "→E", OF Situation.ψ, THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
270    AOT_thus ‹s'[F]›
271      using F_def[symmetric] "rule=E" by blast
272  next
273    fix F
274    AOT_assume 0: ‹s'[F]›
275    AOT_hence ‹∃p (F = [λy p])›
276      using Situation.ψ[THEN situations[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"], THEN "&E"(2),
277                        THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=F], THEN "→E"]
278            "prop-prop1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] by blast
279    then AOT_obtain p where F_def: ‹F = [λy p]›
280      using "∃E" by metis
281    AOT_hence ‹s'[λy p]›
282      using 0 "rule=E" by blast
283    AOT_hence ‹s' ⊨ p›
284      using lem1[THEN "→E", OF Situation.ψ, THEN "≡E"(2)] by blast
285    AOT_hence ‹s ⊨ p›
286      using a[THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=p], THEN "≡E"(2)] by blast
287    AOT_hence ‹s[λy p]›
288      using lem1[THEN "→E", OF Situation.ψ, THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
289    AOT_thus ‹s[F]›
290      using F_def[symmetric] "rule=E" by blast
291  qed
292qed

294AOT_define PartOfSituation :: ‹τ ⇒ τ ⇒ φ› (infixl ‹⊴› 80)
295  "sit-part-whole": ‹s ⊴ s' ≡⇩d⇩f ∀p (s ⊨ p → s' ⊨ p)›
296
297AOT_theorem "part:1": ‹s ⊴ s›
298  by (rule "sit-part-whole"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"])
299     (safe intro!: "&I" Situation.ψ GEN "→I")
300
301AOT_theorem "part:2": ‹s ⊴ s' & s ≠ s' → ¬(s' ⊴ s)›
302proof(rule "→I"; frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2); rule "raa-cor:2")
303  AOT_assume 0: ‹s ⊴ s'›
304  AOT_hence a: ‹s ⊨ p → s' ⊨ p› for p
305    using "∀E"(2) "sit-part-whole"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast
306  AOT_assume ‹s' ⊴ s›
307  AOT_hence b: ‹s' ⊨ p → s ⊨ p› for p
308    using "∀E"(2) "sit-part-whole"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&E" by blast
309  AOT_have ‹∀p (s ⊨ p ≡ s' ⊨ p)›
310    using a b by (simp add: "≡I" "universal-cor")
311  AOT_hence 1: ‹s = s'›
312    using "sit-identity"[THEN "≡E"(2)] by metis
313  AOT_assume ‹s ≠ s'›
314  AOT_hence ‹¬(s = s')›
315    by (metis "≡⇩d⇩fE" "=-infix")
316  AOT_thus ‹s = s' & ¬(s = s')›
317    using 1 "&I" by blast
318qed
319
320AOT_theorem "part:3": ‹s ⊴ s' & s' ⊴ s'' → s ⊴ s''›
321proof(rule "→I"; frule "&E"(1); drule "&E"(2);
322      safe intro!: "&I" GEN "→I" "sit-part-whole"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] Situation.ψ)
323  fix p
324  AOT_assume ‹s ⊨ p›
325  moreover AOT_assume ‹s ⊴ s'›
326  ultimately AOT_have ‹s' ⊨ p›
327    using "sit-part-whole"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", THEN "&E"(2),
328                           THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=p], THEN "→E"] by blast
329  moreover AOT_assume ‹s' ⊴ s''›
330  ultimately AOT_show ‹s'' ⊨ p›
331    using "sit-part-whole"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", THEN "&E"(2),
332                           THEN "∀E"(2)[where β=p], THEN "→E"] by blast
333qed

335AOT_theorem "sit-identity2:1": ‹s = s' ≡ s ⊴ s' & s' ⊴ s›
336proof (safe intro!: "≡I" "&I" "→I")
337  AOT_show ‹s ⊴ s'› if ‹s = s'›
338    using "rule=E" "part:1" that by blast
339next
340  AOT_show ‹s' ⊴ s› if ‹s = s'›
341    using "rule=E" "part:1" that[symmetric] by blast
342next
343  AOT_assume ‹s ⊴ s' & s' ⊴ s›
344  AOT_thus ‹s = s'› using "part:2"[THEN "→E", OF "&I"]
345    by (metis "≡⇩d⇩fI" "&E"(1) "&E"(2) "=-infix" "raa-cor:3")
346qed

348AOT_theorem "sit-identity2:2": ‹s = s' ≡ ∀s'' (s'' ⊴ s ≡ s'' ⊴ s')›
349proof(safe intro!: "≡I" "→I" Situation.GEN "sit-identity"[THEN "≡E"(2)]
350                   GEN[where 'a=𝗈])
351  AOT_show ‹s'' ⊴ s'› if ‹s'' ⊴ s› and ‹s = s'› for s''
352    using "rule=E" that by blast
353next
354  AOT_show ‹s'' ⊴ s› if ‹s'' ⊴ s'› and ‹s = s'› for s''
355    using "rule=E" id_sym that by blast
356next
357  AOT_show ‹s' ⊨ p› if ‹s ⊨ p› and ‹∀s'' (s'' ⊴ s ≡ s'' ⊴ s')› for p
358    using "sit-part-whole"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", THEN "&E"(2),
359              OF that(2)[THEN "Situation.∀E", THEN "≡E"(1), OF "part:1"],
360              THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E", OF that(1)].
361next
362  AOT_show ‹s ⊨ p› if ‹s' ⊨ p› and ‹∀s'' (s'' ⊴ s ≡ s'' ⊴ s')› for p
363    using "sit-part-whole"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE", THEN "&E"(2),
364          OF that(2)[THEN "Situation.∀E", THEN "≡E"(2), OF "part:1"],
365          THEN "∀E"(2), THEN "→E", OF that(1)].
366qed

368AOT_define Persistent :: ‹φ ⇒ φ› (‹Persistent'(_')›)
369  persistent: ‹Persistent(p) ≡⇩d⇩f ∀s (s ⊨ p → ∀s' (s ⊴ s' → s' ⊨ p))›
370

381AOT_theorem "thm-null-trivial:1": ‹∃!x NullSituation(x)›
382proof (AOT_subst ‹NullSituation(x)› ‹A!x & ∀F (x[F] ≡ F ≠ F)› for: x)
383  AOT_modally_strict {
384    AOT_show ‹NullSituation(x) ≡ A!x & ∀F (x[F] ≡ F ≠ F)› for x
385    proof (safe intro!: "≡I" "→I" "df-null-trivial:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"]
386                dest!: "df-null-trivial:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"])
387      AOT_assume 0: ‹Situation(x) & ¬∃p x ⊨ p›
388      AOT_have 1: ‹A!x›
389        using 0[THEN "&E"(1), THEN situations[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"], THEN "&E"(1)].
390      AOT_have 2: ‹x[F] → ∃p F = [λy p]› for F
391        using 0[THEN "&E"(1), THEN situations[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"],
392                THEN "&E"(2), THEN "∀E"(2)]
393        by (metis "≡⇩d⇩fE" "→I" "prop-prop1" "→E")
394      AOT_show ‹A!x & ∀F (x[F] ≡ F ≠ F)›
395      proof (safe intro!: "&I" 1 GEN "≡I" "→I")
396        fix F
397        AOT_assume ‹x[F]›
398        moreover AOT_obtain p where ‹F = [λy p]›
399          using calculation 2[THEN "→E"] "∃E"[rotated] by blast
400        ultimately AOT_have ‹x[λy p]›
401          by (metis "rule=E")
402        AOT_hence ‹x ⊨ p›
403          using lem1[THEN "→E", OF 0[THEN "&E"(1)], THEN "≡E"(2)] by blast
404        AOT_hence ‹∃p (x ⊨ p)›
405          by (rule "∃I")
406        AOT_thus ‹F ≠ F›
407          using 0[THEN "&E"(2)] "raa-cor:1" "&I" by blast
408      next
409        fix F :: ‹<κ> AOT_var›
410        AOT_assume ‹F ≠ F›
411        AOT_hence ‹¬(F = F)› by (metis "≡⇩d⇩fE" "=-infix")
412        moreover AOT_have ‹F = F›
413          by (simp add: "id-eq:1")
414        ultimately AOT_show ‹x[F]› using "&I" "raa-cor:1" by blast
415      qed
416    next
417      AOT_assume 0: ‹A!x & ∀F (x[F] ≡ F ≠ F)›
418      AOT_hence ‹x[F] ≡ F ≠ F› for F
419        using "∀E" "&E" by blast
420      AOT_hence 1: ‹¬x[F]› for F
421        using "≡⇩d⇩fE" "id-eq:1" "=-infix" "reductio-aa:1" "≡E"(1) by blast
422      AOT_show ‹Situation(x) & ¬∃p x ⊨ p›
423      proof (safe intro!: "&I" situations[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] 0[THEN "&E"(1)] GEN "→I")
424        AOT_show ‹Propositional([F])› if ‹x[F]› for F
425          using that 1 "&I" "raa-cor:1" by fast
426      next
427        AOT_show ‹¬∃p x ⊨ p›
428        proof(rule "raa-cor:2")
429          AOT_assume ‹∃p x ⊨ p›
430          then AOT_obtain p where ‹x ⊨ p› using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
431          AOT_hence ‹x[λy p]›
432            using "≡⇩d⇩fE" "&E"(1) "≡E"(1) lem1 "modus-tollens:1"
433                  "raa-cor:3" "true-in-s" by fast
434          moreover AOT_have ‹¬x[λy p]›
435            by (rule 1[unvarify F]) "cqt:2[lambda]"
436          ultimately AOT_show ‹p & ¬p› for p using "&I" "raa-cor:1" by blast
437        qed
438      qed
439    qed
440  }
441next
442  AOT_show ‹∃!x ([A!]x & ∀F (x[F] ≡ F ≠ F))›
443    by (simp add: "A-objects!")
444qed

603    using 0[THEN "&E"(2)] by (metis "→I" "existential:2[const_var]" "raa-cor:3")

652definition ConditionOnPropositionalProperties :: ‹(<κ> ⇒ 𝗈) ⇒ bool› where
653  "cond-prop": ‹ConditionOnPropositionalProperties ≡ λ φ . ∀ v .
654                        [v ⊨ ∀F (φ{F} → Propositional([F]))]›
655
656syntax ConditionOnPropositionalProperties :: ‹id_position ⇒ AOT_prop›
657  ("CONDITION'_ON'_PROPOSITIONAL'_PROPERTIES'(_')")

659AOT_theorem "cond-prop[E]":
660  assumes ‹CONDITION_ON_PROPOSITIONAL_PROPERTIES(φ)›
661  shows ‹∀F (φ{F} → Propositional([F]))›
662  using assms[unfolded "cond-prop"] by auto

664AOT_theorem "cond-prop[I]":
665  assumes ‹❙⊢⇩□ ∀F (φ{F} → Propositional([F]))›
666  shows ‹CONDITION_ON_PROPOSITIONAL_PROPERTIES(φ)›
667  using assms "cond-prop" by metis

669AOT_theorem "pre-comp-sit":
670  assumes ‹CONDITION_ON_PROPOSITIONAL_PROPERTIES(φ)›
671  shows ‹(Situation(x) & ∀F (x[F] ≡ φ{F})) ≡ (A!x & ∀F (x[F] ≡ φ{F}))›
672proof(rule "≡I"; rule "→I")
673  AOT_assume ‹Situation(x) & ∀F (x[F] ≡ φ{F})›
674  AOT_thus ‹A!x & ∀F (x[F] ≡ φ{F})›
675    using "&E" situations[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"] "&I" by blast
676next
677  AOT_assume 0: ‹A!x & ∀F (x[F] ≡ φ{F})›
678  AOT_show ‹Situation(x) & ∀F (x[F] ≡ φ{F})›
679  proof (safe intro!: situations[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I")
680    AOT_show ‹A!x› using 0[THEN "&E"(1)].
681  next
682    AOT_show ‹∀F (x[F] → Propositional([F]))›
683    proof(rule GEN; rule "→I")
684      fix F
685      AOT_assume ‹x[F]›
686      AOT_hence ‹φ{F}›
687        using 0[THEN "&E"(2)] "∀E" "≡E" by blast
688      AOT_thus ‹Propositional([F])›
689        using "cond-prop[E]"[OF assms] "∀E" "→E" by blast
690    qed
691  next
692    AOT_show ‹∀F (x[F] ≡ φ{F})› using 0 "&E" by blast
693  qed
694qed

732AOT_theorem "act-and-not-pos": ‹∃s (Actual(s) & ◇¬Actual(s))›
733proof -
734  AOT_obtain q⇩1 where q⇩1_prop: ‹q⇩1 & ◇¬q⇩1›
735    by (metis "≡⇩d⇩fE" "instantiation" "cont-tf:1" "cont-tf-thm:1")
736  AOT_have ‹∃s (∀F (s[F] ≡ F = [λy q⇩1]))›
737  proof (safe intro!: "comp-sit:1" "cond-prop[I]" GEN "→I")
738    AOT_modally_strict {
739      AOT_show ‹Propositional([F])› if ‹F = [λy q⇩1]› for F
740        using "≡⇩d⇩fI" "existential:2[const_var]" "prop-prop1" that by fastforce
741    }
742  qed
743  then AOT_obtain s⇩1 where s_prop: ‹∀F (s⇩1[F] ≡ F = [λy q⇩1])›
744    using "Situation.∃E"[rotated] by meson
745  AOT_have ‹Actual(s⇩1)›
746  proof(safe intro!: actual[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I" GEN "→I" s_prop Situation.ψ)
747    fix p
748    AOT_assume ‹s⇩1 ⊨ p›
749    AOT_hence ‹s⇩1[λy p]›
750      by (metis "≡⇩d⇩fE" "&E"(2) "prop-enc" "true-in-s")
751    AOT_hence ‹[λy p] = [λy q⇩1]›
752      by (rule s_prop[THEN "∀E"(1), THEN "≡E"(1), rotated]) "cqt:2[lambda]"
753    AOT_hence ‹p = q⇩1› by (metis "≡E"(2) "p-identity-thm2:3")
754    AOT_thus ‹p› using q⇩1_prop[THEN "&E"(1)] "rule=E" id_sym by fast
755  qed
756  moreover AOT_have ‹◇¬Actual(s⇩1)›
757  proof(rule "raa-cor:1"; drule "KBasic:12"[THEN "≡E"(2)])
758    AOT_assume ‹□Actual(s⇩1)›
759    AOT_hence ‹□(Situation(s⇩1) & ∀p (s⇩1 ⊨ p → p))›
760      using actual[THEN "≡Df", THEN "conventions:3"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"],
761                   THEN "&E"(1), THEN RM, THEN "→E"] by blast
762    AOT_hence ‹□∀p (s⇩1 ⊨ p → p)›
763      by (metis "RM:1" "Conjunction Simplification"(2) "→E")
764    AOT_hence ‹∀p □(s⇩1 ⊨ p → p)›
765      by (metis "CBF" "vdash-properties:10")
766    AOT_hence ‹□(s⇩1 ⊨ q⇩1 → q⇩1)›
767      using "∀E" by blast
768    AOT_hence ‹□s⇩1 ⊨ q⇩1 → □q⇩1›
769      by (metis "→E" "qml:1" "vdash-properties:1[2]")
770    moreover AOT_have ‹s⇩1 ⊨ q⇩1›
771      using s_prop[THEN "∀E"(1), THEN "≡E"(2),
772                   THEN lem1[THEN "→E", OF Situation.ψ, THEN "≡E"(2)]]
773            "rule=I:1" "prop-prop2:2" by blast
774    ultimately AOT_have ‹□q⇩1›
775      using "≡⇩d⇩fE" "&E"(1) "≡E"(1) "lem2:1" "true-in-s" "→E" by fast
776    AOT_thus ‹◇¬q⇩1 & ¬◇¬q⇩1›
777      using "KBasic:12"[THEN "≡E"(1)] q⇩1_prop[THEN "&E"(2)] "&I" by blast
778  qed
779  ultimately AOT_have ‹(Actual(s⇩1) & ◇¬Actual(s⇩1))›
780    using s_prop "&I" by blast
781  thus ?thesis
782    by (rule "Situation.∃I")
783qed

833AOT_theorem comp:
834  ‹∃s (s' ⊴ s & s'' ⊴ s & ∀s''' (s' ⊴ s''' & s'' ⊴ s''' → s ⊴ s'''))›
835proof -
836  have cond_prop: ‹ConditionOnPropositionalProperties (λ Π . «s'[Π] ∨ s''[Π]»)›

838        rule "→I")

853        by (simp add: Situation.restricted_var_condition)

858        using "→E" by blast

862    using "comp-sit:1"[OF cond_prop] "Situation.∃E"[rotated] by meson

864  proof(safe intro!: "&I" "≡⇩d⇩fI"[OF "true-in-s"] "≡⇩d⇩fI"[OF "prop-enc"]

880      using θ[THEN "∀E"(1),OF "prop-prop2:2", THEN "≡E"(2), OF "∨I"(2)] by blast
881  next
882    fix s p

884    AOT_assume ‹s⇩3 ⊨ p›
885    AOT_hence ‹s⇩3[λx p]›
886      by (metis "&E"(2) "prop-enc" "≡⇩d⇩fE" "true-in-s")

888      using θ[THEN "∀E"(1),OF "prop-prop2:2", THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
889    moreover {

892        by (safe intro!: "prop-enc"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "true-in-s"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fI"] "&I"

1363    using "comp-sit:1"[OF "cond-prop"].
1364  then AOT_obtain s⇩0 where s⇩0_prop: ‹∀F (s⇩0[F] ≡ ∃q (q & F = [λy q]))›
1365    using "Situation.∃E"[rotated] by meson
1366  AOT_have ‹∀p (s⇩0 ⊨ p ≡ p)›
1367  proof(safe intro!: GEN "≡I" "→I")
1368    fix p
1369    AOT_assume ‹s⇩0 ⊨ p›
1370    AOT_hence ‹s⇩0[λy p]›
1371      using lem1[THEN "→E", OF Situation.ψ, THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
1372    AOT_hence ‹∃q (q & [λy p] = [λy q])›
1373      using s⇩0_prop[THEN "∀E"(1)[rotated, OF "prop-prop2:2"], THEN "≡E"(1)] by blast
1374    then AOT_obtain q⇩1 where q⇩1_prop: ‹q⇩1 & [λy p] = [λy q⇩1]›
1375      using "∃E"[rotated] by blast
1376    AOT_hence ‹p = q⇩1›
1377      by (metis "&E"(2) "≡E"(2) "p-identity-thm2:3")
1378    AOT_thus ‹p›
1379      using q⇩1_prop[THEN "&E"(1)] "rule=E" id_sym by fast
1380  next
1381    fix p
1382    AOT_assume ‹p›
1383    moreover AOT_have ‹[λy p] = [λy p]›
1384      by (simp add: "rule=I:1"[OF "prop-prop2:2"])
1385    ultimately AOT_have ‹p & [λy p] = [λy p]›
1386      using "&I" by blast
1387    AOT_hence ‹∃q (q & [λy p] = [λy q])›
1388      by (rule "∃I")
1389    AOT_hence ‹s⇩0[λy p]›
1390      using s⇩0_prop[THEN "∀E"(1)[rotated, OF "prop-prop2:2"], THEN "≡E"(2)] by blast
1391    AOT_thus ‹s⇩0 ⊨ p›
1392      using lem1[THEN "→E", OF Situation.ψ, THEN "≡E"(2)] by blast
1393  qed
1394  AOT_hence ‹∀p (s⇩0 ⊨ p ≡ p)›
1395    using "&I" by blast
1396  AOT_thus ‹∃s ∀p (s ⊨ p ≡ p)›
1397    by (rule "Situation.∃I")
1398qed

1736AOT_theorem "coherent:1": ‹w ⊨ ¬p ≡ ¬w ⊨ p›
1737proof(safe intro!: "≡I" "→I")
1738  AOT_assume 1: ‹w ⊨ ¬p›
1739  AOT_show ‹¬w ⊨ p›
1740  proof(rule "raa-cor:2")
1741    AOT_assume ‹w ⊨ p›
1742    AOT_hence ‹w ⊨ p & w ⊨ ¬p› using 1 "&I" by blast
1743    AOT_hence ‹∃q (w ⊨ q & w ⊨ ¬q)› by (rule "∃I")
1744    moreover AOT_have ‹¬∃q (w ⊨ q & w ⊨ ¬q)›
1745      using "world-cons:1"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"[OF cons], THEN "&E"(2)].
1746    ultimately AOT_show ‹∃q (w ⊨ q & w ⊨ ¬q) & ¬∃q (w ⊨ q & w ⊨ ¬q)›
1747      using "&I" by blast
1748  qed
1749next
1750  AOT_assume ‹¬w ⊨ p›
1751  AOT_thus ‹w ⊨ ¬p›
1752    using "world-max"[THEN "≡⇩d⇩fE"[OF max], THEN "&E"(2)]
1753    by (metis "∨E"(2) "log-prop-prop:2" "rule-ui:1")
1754qed

1976AOT_theorem "t-at-alpha-strict": ‹❙w⇩α ⊨ p ≡ ❙𝒜p›
1977proof -
1978  AOT_have 0: ‹❙w⇩α = ❙ιw Actual(w)›
1979    using "pre-walpha" "rule-id-df:1[zero]" "w-alpha" by blast
1980  AOT_hence walpha_den: ‹❙w⇩α↓›
1981    by (metis "t=t-proper:1" "vdash-properties:6")

1984  AOT_have walpha_sit: ‹Situation(❙w⇩α)›
1985    by (meson "≡⇩d⇩fE" "alpha-world:2" "&E"(1) max)
1986  {
1987    fix p

1989      using "lem2:4"[unconstrain s] by blast

1991    AOT_hence θ: ‹❙𝒜❙w⇩α ⊨ p›
1992      using 2[unvarify x, OF walpha_den, THEN "→E", OF walpha_sit, THEN "≡E"(2)]
1993      by argo
1994    AOT_have 3: ‹❙𝒜Actual(❙w⇩α)›
1995      using "1" "Act-Basic:2" "&E"(2) "≡E"(1) by blast
1996    AOT_have ‹❙𝒜(Situation(❙w⇩α) & ∀q(❙w⇩α ⊨ q → q))›
1997      apply (AOT_subst (reverse) ‹Situation(❙w⇩α) & ∀q(❙w⇩α ⊨ q → q)› ‹Actual(❙w⇩α)›)
1998       using actual "≡Df" apply blast
1999      by (fact 3)

2004    AOT_hence ‹❙𝒜(❙w⇩α ⊨ p) → ❙𝒜p› by (metis "act-cond" "vdash-properties:10")
2005    AOT_hence ‹❙𝒜p› using θ "→E" by blast
2006  }
2007  AOT_hence 2: ‹❙w⇩α ⊨ p → ❙𝒜p› for p by (rule "→I")
2008  AOT_have walpha_sit: ‹Situation(❙w⇩α)›
2009    using "≡⇩d⇩fE" "alpha-world:2" "&E"(1) max by blast
2010  show ?thesis
2011  proof(safe intro!: "≡I" "→I" 2)
2012    AOT_assume actp: ‹❙𝒜p›
2013    AOT_show ‹❙w⇩α ⊨ p›
